         <abstract id="aspace_b9eaa7b68e2a87a0441fc36426c358d3">Letters from Andrew Jackson Davis, author and spiritualist to William Green, Jr., his benefactor. The letters deal with personal, family, and financial matters as well as Davis' work with spiritualism and healing.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n81092485" source="naf">
               <part>Davis, Andrew Jackson, 1826-1910</part>
